pac, a better syntax for pacman and paru
Usage:
    pac <operation>
    
Operations:
    pac install [package(s)]
    pac uninstall [package(s)]
    pac purge [package(s)]
    pac downgrade [package(s)]
    pac update
    pac refresh --- (refreshing mirrors)
    pac clear cache --- (clearing cache package(s))
    pac clear orphans --- (removing orpahned package(s))
    pac search [package] --- (search package in the official repository and AUR)
    pac list [package] --- (search installed package)
